BUON APPETITO
Recipe for Basil Pesto, Mozzarella & Cherry Tomato Pizza

Ingredients
1 pack pizza base mix, approx 145g
Plain flour for rolling out
1 pot or 2 tbsp. Sacla’ Classic Basil Pesto
125g Buffalo Mozzarella, drained and torn into small pieces
6 cherry tomatoes, halved
1 tbsp. Parmesan, finely grated
1 tbsp. Oregano
Salt & black pepper to taste
A small handful of rocket
Extra virgin olive oil for drizzling
<<<<<<< HEAD
add fresh green peppers (Optional)
